name: DNT
description: DNT is a game token owned by SpaceGuild. It is used for advanced functions of the game, such as strengthening equipment, evolving pets, etc., and is also used as a reward for game competitions. The total circulation is 21 million, of which 10 million are actually in circulation. 3 million are pledged in the game, 1 million are airdropped, and 7 million are liquid mining and staking mining.
